{"title":"老支书下乡","authors":["冯永杰"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":2,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老支书下乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯永杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脸汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩搭旧挎包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开流星步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路皆熟人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风迎面扑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老任务！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问问新农机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用得可顺手？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话音落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手齐舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群老和少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包围老支书——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“新农机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗头足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只嫌数量少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得添百部！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大队里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑满屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书挥钢笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘腿坐床铺——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔尖飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情吐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春色映心扉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光暖肺腑……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}